| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4408 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1f43f9c3-4ef4-542a-92bb-def24f2e193c"
